title: 8 People Dead After Shooting at Atlanta-Area Massage Parlors
author: News4JAX
description: Eight people are dead after shootings at three massage parlors.  The suspect-- caught after a chase in south Georgia tonight. Joy Purdy joins us in the newsroom, with the latest on this breaking news.

localize.title: 亚特兰大地区按摩店遭枪击后8人死亡
localize.description: 三家按摩店发生枪击案，8人死亡。 嫌疑人今晚在乔治亚州南部追捕后被抓获。Joy Purdy在新闻室为我们带来了最新的突发新闻。
